### Bungie API — direct calls for exploring real response shapes.
# VS Code REST Client. Needs BUNGIE_API_KEY in .env (see requests/README.md).
# These are the three public, API-key-only endpoints our sync-service + founder
# check consume. Edit @groupId / @bungieNetId to point at a real clan / account.

@bungieBase = https://www.bungie.net/Platform
@groupId = 4683673
@bungieNetId = 19626321

### GetGroup — basic clan info (S1 cron + publish/edit snapshot + preview)
GET {{bungieBase}}/GroupV2/{{groupId}}/
X-API-Key: {{$dotenv BUNGIE_API_KEY}}

### GetMembersOfGroup — member list (S2 cron)
GET {{bungieBase}}/GroupV2/{{groupId}}/Members/
X-API-Key: {{$dotenv BUNGIE_API_KEY}}

### GetGroupsForMember — founder check (login + publish/edit verification)
# membershipType 254 = Bungie.net. Returns the user's clan(s) + isFounder-ish data.
GET {{bungieBase}}/GroupV2/User/254/{{bungieNetId}}/0/1/
X-API-Key: {{$dotenv BUNGIE_API_KEY}}
